===  somp: Simple Open Music Player  ===

This is a free software music player that will automatically download free
(Creative commons or the like) music and play it for you. It will adjust the
music to your tastes as you rate the songs it plays.

Status: Under development. Not useful yet.


Done:
       * Skin you can edit in Inkscape, that's automagically converted to PNGs and C code.
       * GUI mostly finished, including playback, seeking, etc.

To Do:
       * Ratings server interraction
       * Download, play and save tracks
